            <title><![CDATA[‘대부’의 장남, 배우 제임스 칸 별세]]></title>
            <link>https://www.khan.co.kr/culture/movie/article/202207081127001/?utm_campaign=list_click&amp;utm_source=reporter_article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%80%ED%95%98_%EA%B8%B0%EC%9E%90%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80</link>
